Polynomial - Class in br.labsec.thesis.polynomials
An immutable polynomial in the finite field GF(2^k) Supports standard arithmetic in the field, as well as reducibility tests.

Polynomial.Reducibility - Enum in br.labsec.thesis.polynomials
An enumeration representing the reducibility of the polynomial A polynomial p(x) in GF(2^k) is called irreducible over GF[2^k] if it is non-constant and cannot be represented as the product of two or more non-constant polynomials from GF(2^k).
